Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.79,0:02:46.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伯爵
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.86,0:02:48.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿尔贝
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.35,0:02:50.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发生什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.35,0:02:52.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她身体稍有不适
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.53,0:02:55.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,海黛不大习惯人群
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.38,0:02:58.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请您不必顾虑
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.42,0:03:00.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,容后再聚
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.68,0:03:20.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.81,0:03:30.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,海黛小姐看到了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.67,0:03:33.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个时候 她…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.54,0:03:46.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看到了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.67,0:03:49.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个男人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.33,0:04:02.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听说您已有婚约
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.02,0:04:06.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.41,0:04:10.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您幸福吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.74,0:04:19.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在下… 今晚似乎无法控制自己
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.15,0:04:24.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起 我失陪了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.49,0:04:27.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事吧 海黛小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.57,0:04:31.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伯爵的情人你就别管了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.72,0:04:33.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她不是那样的人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.98,0:04:36.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伯爵非常重视她
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.61,0:04:38.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过是疼爱宠物一般
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.10,0:04:41.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要把伯爵和那种人混为一谈
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.01,0:04:43.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伯爵和海黛小姐…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.96,0:04:48.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是已经自立的成人间的关系
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.40,0:04:51.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,互相重视对方…\N
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.81,0:04:53.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,\N不要谈别人了 你自己呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.59,0:04:55.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,关于欧仁妮
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.23,0:05:00.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这点你别说我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.38,0:05:04.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,贵族不是为了爱
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.36,0:05:08.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而是为了金钱和名誉而结婚吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.97,0:05:11.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还在介意那家伙说的话吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.47,0:05:15.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被他说中了 虽然很不甘心
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.29,0:05:18.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结婚不就是那回事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.14,0:05:21.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也不愿意这样…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.61,0:05:26.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弗朗兹·德·埃皮奈男爵
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.93,0:05:27.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望能和您谈谈
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.02,0:05:39.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么不陪伴在她身边
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.32,0:05:41.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和您没关系吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.17,0:05:44.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您不爱她吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.73,0:05:50.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我喜欢她 当她是一位淑女
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.86,0:05:53.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太过分了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.38,0:05:55.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 马克西米利安
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.70,0:05:57.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里交给我 好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.98,0:06:01.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是她的未婚夫 就该认真爱她
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.04,0:06:06.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那种说法也…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.09,0:06:08.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说了实话而已
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.41,0:06:10.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太过激了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.52,0:06:12.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然一直如此…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.34,0:06:16.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也一样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.23,0:06:20.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有像他那样真心爱上某人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.02,0:06:22.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿尔贝
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.08,0:06:27.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爱一个人是怎么样的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.20,0:06:30.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真伤脑筋
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.45,0:06:40.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这件事就拜托你了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.50,0:06:45.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.81,0:06:55.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们走
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.03,0:07:03.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是算了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.29,0:07:05.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事到如今你还说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.58,0:07:07.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要按计划进行 一切都会很顺利
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.55,0:07:11.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,首先你赞美她
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.59,0:07:12.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赞美？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.83,0:07:14.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赞美什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.82,0:07:16.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么都行
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.36,0:07:17.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,服饰啊 打扮啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.41,0:07:26.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,维尔福首席检察官 是瓦朗蒂娜的父亲
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.06,0:07:29.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很令人畏惧吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.52,0:07:32.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果落入他的手里 小偷都会被判死刑
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.57,0:07:41.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是瓦朗蒂娜的母亲
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.84,0:07:43.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然她们没有血缘关系
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.97,0:07:47.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爱德华 快过来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.81,0:07:49.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要不要\N
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.31,0:07:51.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,\N弟弟爱德华 和瓦朗蒂娜是同父异母的姐弟
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.61,0:07:52.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.91,0:07:56.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看 很漂亮的马吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.62,0:07:58.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我讨厌马
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.42,0:08:00.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.67,0:08:02.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他太任性了 真是丢脸
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.12,0:08:04.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瓦朗蒂娜呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.71,0:08:08.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那孩子说留在家里比较合她的个性
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.16,0:08:10.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也讨厌瓦朗蒂娜
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.04,0:08:25.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差不多该来了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.34,0:08:52.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没事 祖父
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.58,0:08:53.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.80,0:08:58.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿尔贝·德·莫尔塞夫子爵前来拜访
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.13,0:09:02.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.41,0:09:09.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨晚…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.60,0:09:15.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他似乎有话对你说
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.38,0:09:18.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.10,0:09:20.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 那个
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.22,0:09:24.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起 我要去准备祖父的午饭
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.79,0:09:27.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.80,0:09:29.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您…您…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.87,0:09:33.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我爱上您了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.51,0:09:37.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我喜欢您
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.89,0:09:42.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是 顺序全乱了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.17,0:09:45.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了 先让我来说
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.66,0:09:48.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你到一边待着
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.60,0:09:49.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我喜欢您
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.62,0:09:51.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.71,0:09:55.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让您受惊了 抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.41,0:09:57.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不该这样的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.63,0:09:59.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是在揶揄我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.04,0:10:03.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是 是认真的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.65,0:10:06.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然这样 什么意思
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.16,0:10:08.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,马克西米利安是认真的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.39,0:10:13.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然 他表现得有点笨拙
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.07,0:10:15.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不想听这些
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.35,0:10:17.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.95,0:10:24.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我问过弗朗兹
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.33,0:10:31.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弗朗兹对您的感觉只是父母定下的对象
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.90,0:10:35.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是您也是这样吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.85,0:10:41.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以只要像他对您一样对他就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.66,0:10:42.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然没有爵位
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.16,0:10:45.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,马克西米利安是位出色的军人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.62,0:10:46.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是一个率直的男人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.35,0:10:50.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且最重要的是他深爱着您
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.79,0:10:52.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定会让您幸福的…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.78,0:10:53.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请回去
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.15,0:10:59.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家…大家都如此自私
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.69,0:11:01.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瓦朗蒂娜
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.30,0:11:04.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请出去
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.32,0:11:14.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在宣布判决
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.77,0:11:21.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被告犯盗窃及侮辱贵族罪 予以死刑
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.48,0:11:23.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请您酌情处理
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.39,0:11:25.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有同情的余地
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.70,0:11:32.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,扰乱王国的秩序 这些垃圾
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.43,0:11:50.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有探访
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.40,0:11:56.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗨 还眷恋尘世吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.14,0:12:02.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和瓦朗蒂娜相处得还好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.74,0:12:07.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听说你对她很冷淡哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.92,0:12:10.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底是谁这么说
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.90,0:12:11.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是传闻
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.86,0:12:16.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已经很关心她了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.11,0:12:20.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就因为她是前妻的女儿 就这样…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.37,0:12:27.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说 速度是不是太快了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.48,0:12:28.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…夫人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.47,0:12:33.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,马…马不听使唤了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.07,0:13:02.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.68,0:13:07.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,基督山伯爵
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.98,0:13:13.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多亏您 我们才逃过一劫
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.41,0:13:19.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正好有善于驯马的人在场
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.00,0:13:20.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪的脸
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.64,0:13:23.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是宇宙人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.87,0:13:26.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.87,0:13:30.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好奇心是聪明的标志
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.94,0:13:33.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还没请教您的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.87,0:13:36.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这位是基督山伯爵
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.60,0:13:40.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和外子亲如家人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.93,0:13:45.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听说您买下了过世的王子的看台
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.51,0:13:47.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说来惭愧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.70,0:13:51.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正是这种事情令我引人注目
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.89,0:13:53.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但只是因为没有其他座位了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.95,0:13:58.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这位是维尔福首席检察官的夫人埃洛伊丝
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.33,0:14:02.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没想到是巴黎守护神的尊夫人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.01,0:14:05.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您真会说话
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.36,0:14:10.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,马的情绪还很不稳定
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.12,0:14:12.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我护送您回家吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.23,0:14:18.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,维尔福夫人 不介意的话可乘我的车同行
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.14,0:14:25.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一次看见那样的她
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.97,0:14:33.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夫人回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.39,0:14:36.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,马克西米利安
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.82,0:14:41.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巴鲁瓦 为客人准备茶点
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.46,0:14:43.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请不用客气 夫人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.59,0:14:50.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请叫我埃洛伊丝 伯爵
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.39,0:14:58.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瓦朗蒂娜 有客人来了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.83,0:15:02.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小姐心情不佳
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.30,0:15:04.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.58,0:15:09.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瓦朗蒂娜 跟客人打个招呼都不行吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.49,0:15:10.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瓦朗蒂娜
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.11,0:15:15.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她真是出奇的不幸
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.60,0:15:17.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.76,0:15:23.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白 她从心底里渴望自由
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.72,0:15:26.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但只能逃避真心
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.15,0:15:28.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.84,0:15:30.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她很敏感 容易受伤
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.32,0:15:33.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你听不到她灵魂的叫喊吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.45,0:15:35.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我听到了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.52,0:15:37.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说大家都如此自私
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.52,0:15:40.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是 你也是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.49,0:15:42.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个也是 那个也是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.59,0:15:49.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那孩子总是这样让我烦恼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.48,0:15:52.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像她去世的母亲
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.82,0:15:54.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柔弱 又封闭
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.72,0:15:59.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了让她善于社交 我也在付出努力
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.12,0:16:04.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈说过她一定会早死
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.00,0:16:07.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爱德华 尽说瞎话
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.87,0:16:12.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是这孩子也很不幸
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.83,0:16:16.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瓦朗蒂娜继承了祖父诺瓦蒂埃卿
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.94,0:16:19.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和娘家圣·梅朗侯爵家的遗产
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.79,0:16:22.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是这孩子什么也没有
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.22,0:16:25.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真可怜
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.98,0:16:31.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使没有血缘关系 姐弟也应当同等幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.03,0:16:37.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这家伙像个吸血鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.33,0:16:39.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爱德华 我要生气了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.39,0:16:41.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吸血鬼 吸血鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.94,0:16:45.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一脸青白的吸血鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.94,0:16:47.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是没礼貌的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.90,0:16:50.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 很可爱的小少爷
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.59,0:16:56.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了赔礼 我带您去我的秘密花园吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.51,0:17:01.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,微不起眼的隐秘之处
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.87,0:17:06.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真担心她
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.18,0:17:10.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但现在的我什么也…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.50,0:17:17.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.84,0:17:24.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没想到藏着一个温室
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.12,0:17:26.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太美了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.65,0:17:27.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.35,0:17:32.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能只有花草才是我的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.22,0:17:38.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}{\fs20}Belladonna、Mandragora、Datura：均为有毒植物
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.22,0:17:36.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,颠茄 曼陀罗 洋金花
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.44,0:17:42.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夫人喜爱的花有一种迷人的共同点
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.96,0:17:43.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.11,0:17:49.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都在美艳的花朵之下隐藏着毒物
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.00,0:17:53.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我都没有注意到
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.77,0:17:55.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.43,0:18:00.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由于喜爱园艺 对植物学也颇有爱好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.87,0:18:02.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身为女人有这种兴趣真是惭愧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.71,0:18:08.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莫非您对毒物也感兴趣
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.06,0:18:11.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会 那太可怕了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.08,0:18:13.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可怕？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.36,0:18:14.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.07,0:18:17.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毒物学与药物学如同表里
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.30,0:18:23.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有什么比毒物更诱人的了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.37,0:18:25.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.09,0:18:29.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞬间致人死地的毒
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.59,0:18:33.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逐渐起效 完全不留痕迹的毒
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.39,0:18:37.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多少严重的毒杀案件
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.16,0:18:41.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都不为人知地埋没于黑夜中
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.31,0:18:44.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有一点
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.94,0:18:48.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被毒迷住的人是美丽的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.24,0:18:54.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偷窥可不是绅士该干的…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.62,0:19:01.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}{\fs20}Borgia：15世纪的博尔吉亚，堪称最早的黑手党家族。
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.62,0:19:01.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是俗称「博尔吉亚之戒」的工艺品
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.84,0:19:05.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来 按下那颗宝石
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.64,0:19:11.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}{\fs20}Lucrezia Borgia：博尔吉亚家族闻名遐尔的黑手党
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.64,0:19:09.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,据闻卢克利齐娅·博尔吉亚用这个
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.13,0:19:13.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,葬送了无数性命
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.61,0:19:17.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那其中包括她的丈夫
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.37,0:19:21.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这枚戒指是夫人您的了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.54,0:19:24.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好高兴
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.08,0:19:28.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是一点见面礼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.99,0:19:50.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祖父
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.33,0:19:56.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想远离这个地方
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.96,0:20:01.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没人认识我的远方
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.33,0:20:16.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真伤脑筋
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.13,0:20:27.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,贝内代托 看左边
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.11,0:20:30.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是阿尔贝·德·莫尔塞夫子爵
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.33,0:21:41.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在伯爵的别墅举行的聚会
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.15,0:21:43.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身处迷宫中的我们
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.80,0:21:46.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,与华丽而可怕的过去擦肩而过
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.17,0:21:48.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下回 岩窟王
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.49,0:21:50.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第八话\N布洛涅之夜
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.22,0:21:52.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等待 然后期待
